@page "/help"

<PageTitle>Help | TicketConsolidator</PageTitle>

<div class="help-container animate-fade-in">
    <div class="glass-panel content-card">
        <h2 class="page-title">Help & Documentation</h2>
        
        <div class="help-section">
            <h3>Overview</h3>
            <p>TicketConsolidator helps you package SQL scripts from Outlook emails into a release-ready format.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="help-section">
            <h3>How to Use</h3>
            <ol class="steps-list">
                <li class="animate-slide-right" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
                    <span class="step-marker animate-pulse">1</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Find Scripts:</strong> Enter a Ticket Number (e.g. <code>12345</code> or <code>ABC-123</code>) and click "Scan".
                        <p class="step-desc">The app searches your configured Outlook folder for emails with that ticket number and extracts attached SQL files.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="animate-slide-right" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
                    <span class="step-marker animate-pulse">2</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Review & Reorder:</strong> The extracted scripts appear in lists (Tables, PROCs, Data).
                        <p class="step-desc">Drag and drop or use arrows to reorder them if execution order matters.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="animate-slide-right" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
                    <span class="step-marker animate-pulse">3</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Manual Upload:</strong> Drag scripts directly from your desktop into the upload zone effectively adding them to the list.
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="animate-slide-right" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
                    <span class="step-marker animate-pulse">4</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Consolidate:</strong> Click "Consolidate & Save" to merge all scripts into one master SQL file.
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="animate-slide-right" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">
                    <span class="step-marker animate-pulse">5</span>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <strong>Release:</strong> Click "Create Release Email" to generate a draft email in Outlook with the consolidated scripts attached.
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="help-section">
             <h3>Troubleshooting</h3>
             <ul class="trouble-list">
                 <li><strong>Outlook Error:</strong> Ensure default Outlook (Desktop) is running. "New Outlook" (Web wrapper) is not supported.</li>
                 <li><strong>Scan Failed:</strong> Check "Settings" to ensure the Target Folder name matches your Outlook folder exactly.</li>
             </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer-info">
            <p>Version 2.0.0 (Blazor Edition)</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .help-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .content-card { padding: 3rem; }
    
    .help-section { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    
    h3 { 
        color: var(--primary); 
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); 
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem; 
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    p { line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-primary); }
    
    .steps-list { 
        padding-left: 0; 
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .steps-list li { 
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        opacity: 0; /* Starts hidden for animation */
    }
    
    .step-marker {
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--primary-glow);
    }
    
    .step-content { flex: 1; padding-top: 0.25rem; }
    
    .steps-list strong { color: #a5b4fc; } /* Lighter accent */
    
    .step-desc { 
        margin-top: 0.25rem; 
        font-size: 0.9rem; 
        color: var(--text-secondary); 
    }
    
    .trouble-list li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    .trouble-list strong { color: #f87171; }
    
    .footer-info {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        padding-top: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }
    
    code { 
        background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); 
        padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem; 
        border-radius: 4px; 
        font-family: monospace;
    }
</style>
